title: Censused shall mean those slums located on lands belonging to Govt
clause_text: Censused shall mean those slums located on lands belonging to Govt., any undertaking of Govt., or MCGM and incorporated in the records of land owning authority as having been censused in 1976, 1980, 1985, 1995 or prior to 1st Jan 2000.
